9 That is correct .	Your order will be ready at the next counter , Laura .
10 Cheers !	Have a nice day !

5 Large cup .	Would you like anything else with that ?
6 That is it .	So that would be a large latte . Is that right ?
7 Can I have medium , please ?	Sure ! So that would be a medium latte . Is that right ?
8 Indeed !	Your order will be ready at the next counter , Kiefer .
9 Goodbye !	Have a nice day !

9 Indeed !	Your order will be ready at the next counter , Lea .
10 Have a nice day !	Have a nice day !

7 Can I get medium ?	Sure ! So that would be a medium cappuccino and a slice of banana bread . Is that right ?
8 Indeed !	Your order will be ready at the next counter , Timothy .
9 Bye !	Have a nice day !

5 Medium cup .	Would you like anything else with that ?

8 Indeed !	Your order will be ready at the next counter , Simon .
9 Have a great day !	Have a nice day !
